title: #217: Rocket Man (@FahimAnwar)
itunes:title: Rocket Man with Fahim Anwar
description: Fahim Anwar met me at Benji's place while I was in LA and we talked about his career as an aerospace engineer. It's a long way from that to Guy Code. Man. Join us as we sat outside and brough Arab and Jew together. (Fahim insists he's not an Arab)
